WEBVTT

00:05.521 --> 00:07.604
<i>Previously on</i>
<i>Masters Of Sex...</i>

00:07.636 --> 00:09.953
Austin: Allow me to introduce
my wife, Celeste.

00:09.988 --> 00:11.454
Helen:
All I want is a baby.

00:11.489 --> 00:12.772
Austin: She doesn't have anyone
to have it with.

00:12.807 --> 00:14.257
She asked me for my help.

00:14.292 --> 00:16.292
Paul: It's Joy.
She collapsed.

00:16.328 --> 00:18.728
And they're calling it
a brain aneurysm.

00:18.730 --> 00:20.280
Paul: What do you want from me?

00:20.315 --> 00:21.564
These past few months,

00:21.616 --> 00:23.566
all I have wanted to see
come through that door is you.

00:23.568 --> 00:26.069
Libby: I can't give you
any more of myself

00:26.071 --> 00:28.304
because I have already
given it all.

00:28.340 --> 00:30.039
Libby: Your son was beaten up
at school.

00:30.075 --> 00:31.741
William: Yeah, that's why
you lash out at other boys--

00:31.743 --> 00:34.077
boys who are smarter than you,
better than you.

00:34.079 --> 00:35.578
Because you're stupid.

00:35.580 --> 00:37.463
William: Look, Dennis,
I owe you an apology.

00:37.499 --> 00:38.631
You're a hell of a player.

00:38.667 --> 00:40.183
You could be playing
for Nebraska one day,

00:40.218 --> 00:41.668
like Coach Edley.

00:42.721 --> 00:44.804
William: Uh, you're here
for the surrogacy program?

00:44.839 --> 00:46.172
Nora:
I'm not squeamish about sex,

00:46.224 --> 00:47.674
if that's what you're thinking.

00:47.726 --> 00:49.142
Betty:
Virginia and I talked about

00:49.177 --> 00:50.677
the surrogacy business
last week,

00:50.729 --> 00:53.062
and she didn't sound
exactly full steam ahead.

00:53.098 --> 00:56.099
Virginia: And what we'll be
experimenting with, hopefully,

00:56.101 --> 00:57.400
is the subliminal scent.

00:57.435 --> 00:59.335
Both:
The holy grail of attraction.

01:00.405 --> 01:02.205
William: Is the cough
in your throat or your chest?

01:02.240 --> 01:03.506
Virginia:
A little bit of both.

01:03.541 --> 01:05.541
I think that I'll be fine
as soon as I get out of bed.

01:05.577 --> 01:07.493
Dan:
How did the good doctor take it?

01:07.529 --> 01:10.079
Virginia: Surprisingly well.

01:10.115 --> 01:12.215
William: Dan Logan's study
has reached a dead end.

01:12.250 --> 01:15.034
