why <i> you</i> were so quiet.

02:42.290 --> 02:46.759
Dan: Because I'm trying to find
a reason to stay.

02:46.795 --> 02:49.962
Here. In St. Louis.

02:53.184 --> 02:56.552
Look, I came to you
to bottle the smell of sex,

02:56.621 --> 02:58.054
