are still erratic.

03:07.615 --> 03:08.898
I know.

03:08.900 --> 03:10.867
Some women get aroused,
some don't.

03:10.902 --> 03:12.902
Dan: Hm. 75% don't.

03:14.672 --> 03:17.907
Virginia:
So... you're leaving?

03:20.145 --> 03:21.277
Dan: [ Sighs ]

03:23.465 --> 03:24.747
Virginia: Well...

03:24.799 --> 03:27.083
that explains
the lack of vocalization.

03:27.085 --> 03:28.751
It's not exactly the right time

03:28.803 --> 03:31.637
to get in the habit
of blurting out the wrong name.

03:31.673 --> 03:34.140
Dan: There are no other names,
Virginia.

03:34.175 --> 03:36.626
Virginia: And your wife?

03:39.764 --> 03:42.532
Dan: My wife and I haven't
called out each other's names

03:42.567 --> 03:43.733
in a very long time...

03:44.869 --> 03:48.237
or occupied the same bed.

03:48.273 --> 03:50.106
We...

03:51.609 --> 03:53.993
Well, you and George
have an arrangement, right?

03:54.028 --> 03:55.945
My wife and I have
an understanding.

03:55.947 --> 03:57.446
Virginia: But...

04:01.503 --> 04:05.788
You <i> want</i> to stay in St. Louis?

04:05.790 --> 04:09.926
Even though nothing's
going to change, obviously,

04:09.961 --> 04:14.797
in our respective
circumstances?

04:14.833 --> 04:17.433
I'm just curious.

04:17.468 --> 04:19.168
Dan: I want to stay.

04:21.805 --> 04:23.573
But I don't know if I can.

04:37.055 --> 04:38.321
Virginia: [ Sighs ]

04:40.074 --> 04:41.424
William: [ Clears throat ]

04:41.459 --> 04:45.061
Virginia: Jesus!

04:45.096 --> 04:46.395
Bill, you startled me.

04:46.431 --> 04:49.332
William: I-I tried calling you,
you know, several times.

04:49.367 --> 04:51.567
Virginia:
So, I don't pick up the phone,

04:51.636 --> 04:53.903
and your solution is
to drive over here?

04:53.938 --> 04:56.839
William: I didn't know
where you were.

04:56.875 --> 05:00.376
Virginia:
Dropping off my children

05:00.411 --> 05:02.912
and dealing with George--

05:02.947 --> 05:05.314
not that I have to
explain that to you.

05:05.350 --> 05:08.451
William:
I didn't say you did.

05:08.486 --> 05:12.121
I-- I'm--
I suppose I'm not myself.

05:16.794 --> 05:17.927
Virginia: [ Sighs ]

05:17.962 --> 05:21.063
The Whitners have an intake
at 8:00 AM,

05:21.099 --> 05:24.066
so I have to be at work
early tomorrow.

05:24.102 --> 05:26.836
William: Virginia, I'm sorry.

05:29.574 --> 05:31.274
I'm sorry you're still angry.

05:31.309 --> 05:33.743
Virginia:
How else should I feel, Bill?

05:33.778 --> 05:35.144
I'm out sick and you go

05:35.179 --> 05:38.047
and set up the surrogacy program
behind my back!

05:38.099 --> 05:40.883
William: I-I know.
You're right. You're right.

05:40.885 --> 05:45.221
I shouldn't have taken matters
into my own hands in that way--

05:45.223 --> 05:47.556
with the surrogacy program or...

05:51.396 --> 05:53.229
any number of things.

05:53.231 --> 05:54.614
Virginia: Other things.

05:54.649 --> 05:56.649
In the past.

05:58.903 --> 06:01.137
That affect my kids.

06:09.280 --> 06:11.497
William: I'm asking you
to forgive me...

06:14.919 --> 06:19.255
and, uh,
to keep an open mind.

06:19.257 --> 06:21.590
Please.

06:27.181 --> 06:28.564
Because...

06:30.435 --> 06:33.486
Because I-I--
I can't think straight

06:33.521 --> 06:37.857
when we're estranged
like this--

06:37.909 --> 06:41.694
you know, when--
when we're not together.

06:41.746 --> 06:43.446
Virginia: We are together.

06:45.033 --> 06:47.616
Bill, of course.

06:47.669 --> 06:49.251
When are we ever not together?

06:49.287 --> 06:51.687
William: No, together in--
in that way.

07:08.690 --> 07:10.306
[ Zipper unzips ]

07:14.529 --> 07:18.748
Virginia, I-I don't want
your hand or your mouth on me.

07:18.783 --> 07:20.349
Virginia:
What man doesn't want that?

07:20.385 --> 07:22.418
William: I want you.

07:22.453 --> 07:24.620
Upstairs.

07:26.240 --> 07:28.240
The way we've always been.

07:33.798 --> 07:37.299
[ Moaning ]

07:37.335 --> 07:39.835
Oh, God.
I missed you so much.

07:39.887 --> 07:42.138
I missed being inside you.

07:42.173 --> 07:43.889
I'm close. Are you close?

07:43.925 --> 07:45.474
Virginia: Yes. Yes.

07:45.510 --> 07:47.259
William: - Can I do something?
Virginia: - No, nothing.

07:47.311 --> 07:49.895
I'm almost there. Don't stop.

07:49.931 --> 07:52.231
Don't stop. Don't stop.

07:52.266 --> 07:56.185
William: [ Moaning ]

07:56.187 --> 08:00.940
[ Both moaning ]

08:00.992 --> 08:03.993
[ Both breathing heavily ]

08:12.453 --> 08:13.702
Virginia: All better?

08:13.704 --> 08:16.705
