08:53.544 --> 08:55.294
Paul:
I hope I'm not intruding.

08:55.329 --> 08:57.163
Libby: No, no. I...

08:57.215 --> 08:59.548
I was just leaving flowers
for Joy and...

09:03.421 --> 09:04.587
Paul: That's your Robert?

09:07.592 --> 09:09.091
I'm so sorry for your loss.

09:09.143 --> 09:11.560
I don't suppose
anyone said that to you.

09:13.314 --> 09:14.930
Libby: No one.

09:14.932 --> 09:17.316
No one knew.

09:17.351 --> 09:18.767
Except you.

09:21.272 --> 09:23.439
Paul: I've missed you, Libby.

09:23.441 --> 09:26.442
You won't so much as look at me
since Joy died.

09:26.494 --> 09:28.611
Libby:
Paul, Joy was my friend,

09:28.663 --> 09:31.697
